{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"For years I've been feeling frustrated,"},{"time":4000,"text":"because as a religious historian,"},{"time":7000,"text":"I've become acutely aware"},{"time":9000,"text":"of the centrality of compassion"},{"time":12000,"text":"in all the major world faiths."},{"time":15000,"text":"Every single one of them"},{"time":17000,"text":"has evolved their own version"},{"time":19000,"text":"of what's been called the Golden Rule."},{"time":22000,"text":"Sometimes it comes in a positive version --"},{"time":25000,"text":"\"Always treat all others as you'd like to be treated yourself.\""},{"time":29000,"text":"And equally important"},{"time":31000,"text":"is the negative version --"},{"time":34000,"text":"\"Don't do to others what you would not like them to do to you.\""},{"time":39000,"text":"Look into your own heart,"},{"time":41000,"text":"discover what it is that gives you pain"},{"time":44000,"text":"and then refuse, under any circumstance whatsoever,"},{"time":48000,"text":"to inflict that pain on anybody else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52000,"text":"And people have emphasized the importance of compassion,"},{"time":57000,"text":"not just because it sounds good,"},{"time":59000,"text":"but because it works."},{"time":62000,"text":"People have found that when they have"},{"time":65000,"text":"implemented the Golden Rule"},{"time":67000,"text":"as Confucius said, \"all day and every day,\""},{"time":71000,"text":"not just a question of doing your good deed for the day"},{"time":73000,"text":"and then returning to a life of greed"},{"time":76000,"text":"and egotism,"},{"time":78000,"text":"but to do it all day and every day,"},{"time":81000,"text":"you dethrone yourself from the center of your world,"},{"time":85000,"text":"put another there, and you transcend yourself."},{"time":88000,"text":"And it brings you into the presence"},{"time":91000,"text":"of what's been called God, Nirvana, Rama, Tao."},{"time":95000,"text":"Something that goes beyond"},{"time":97000,"text":"what we know in our ego-bound existence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"But you know you'd never know it a lot of the time,"},{"time":104000,"text":"that this was so central to the religious life."},{"time":107000,"text":"Because with a few wonderful exceptions,"},{"time":110000,"text":"very often when religious people come together,"},{"time":113000,"text":"religious leaders come together, they're arguing about abstruse doctrines"},{"time":119000,"text":"or uttering a council of hatred"},{"time":123000,"text":"or inveighing against homosexuality or something of that sort."},{"time":128000,"text":"Often people don't really want to be compassionate."},{"time":130000,"text":"I sometimes see"},{"time":132000,"text":"when I'm speaking to a congregation of religious people"},{"time":135000,"text":"a sort of mutinous expression crossing their faces"},{"time":138000,"text":"because people often want to be right instead."},{"time":142000,"text":"And that of course defeats the object of the exercise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146000,"text":"Now why was I so grateful to TED?"},{"time":150000,"text":"Because they took me very gently"},{"time":156000,"text":"from my book-lined study"},{"time":159000,"text":"and brought me into the 21st century,"},{"time":161000,"text":"enabling me to speak to a much, much wider audience"},{"time":165000,"text":"than I could have ever conceived."},{"time":167000,"text":"Because I feel an urgency about this."},{"time":170000,"text":"If we don't manage to implement"},{"time":173000,"text":"the Golden Rule globally,"},{"time":177000,"text":"so that we treat all peoples, wherever and whoever they may be,"},{"time":181000,"text":"as though they were as important as ourselves,"},{"time":184000,"text":"I doubt that we'll have"},{"time":186000,"text":"a viable world to hand on to the next generation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189000,"text":"The task of our time,"},{"time":191000,"text":"one of the great tasks of our time,"},{"time":194000,"text":"is to build a global society, as I said,"},{"time":196000,"text":"where people can live together in peace."},{"time":199000,"text":"And the religions that should be making a major contribution"},{"time":203000,"text":"are instead seen as part of the problem."},{"time":207000,"text":"And of course it's not just religious people who believe in the Golden Rule."},{"time":213000,"text":"This is the source of all morality,"},{"time":216000,"text":"this imaginative act of empathy,"},{"time":219000,"text":"putting yourself in the place of another."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222000,"text":"And so we have a choice, it seems to me."},{"time":226000,"text":"We can either go on bringing out or emphasizing"},{"time":231000,"text":"the dogmatic and intolerant aspects of our faith,"},{"time":235000,"text":"or we can go back to"},{"time":239000,"text":"the rabbis. Rabbi Hillel, the older contemporary of Jesus,"},{"time":244000,"text":"who, when asked by a pagan"},{"time":247000,"text":"to sum up the whole of Jewish teaching while he stood on one leg,"},{"time":252000,"text":"said, \"That which is hateful to you, do not do to your neighbor."},{"time":256000,"text":"That is the Torah and everything else is only commentary.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":261000,"text":"And the rabbis and the early fathers of the church who said that"},{"time":265000,"text":"any interpretation of scripture"},{"time":268000,"text":"that bred hatred and disdain was illegitimate."},{"time":272000,"text":"And we need to revive that spirit."},{"time":275000,"text":"And it's not just going to happen"},{"time":277000,"text":"because a spirit of love wafts us down."},{"time":280000,"text":"We have to make this happen,"},{"time":282000,"text":"and we can do it"},{"time":284000,"text":"with the modern communications"},{"time":286000,"text":"that TED has introduced."},{"time":288000,"text":"Already I've been tremendously heartened"},{"time":291000,"text":"at the response of all our partners."}]},{"cues":[{"time":294000,"text":"In Singapore, we have a group"},{"time":298000,"text":"going to use the Charter to heal divisions"},{"time":302000,"text":"recently that have sprung up in Singaporean society,"},{"time":306000,"text":"and some members of the parliament want"},{"time":309000,"text":"to implement it politically."},{"time":312000,"text":"In Malaysia, there is going to be an art exhibition"},{"time":316000,"text":"in which leading artists are going to be"},{"time":319000,"text":"taking people, young people,"},{"time":323000,"text":"and showing them that compassion also lies"},{"time":325000,"text":"at the root of all art."},{"time":328000,"text":"Throughout Europe, the Muslim communities"},{"time":332000,"text":"are holding events and discussions,"},{"time":335000,"text":"are discussing the centrality of compassion"},{"time":338000,"text":"in Islam and in all faiths."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340000,"text":"But it can't stop there. It can't stop with the launch."},{"time":343000,"text":"Religious teaching, this is where we've gone so wrong,"},{"time":346000,"text":"concentrating solely on believing abstruse doctrines."},{"time":350000,"text":"Religious teaching must always lead to action."},{"time":355000,"text":"And I intend to work on this till my dying day."},{"time":359000,"text":"And I want to continue with our partners"},{"time":364000,"text":"to do two things --"},{"time":366000,"text":"educate and stimulate compassionate thinking."},{"time":373000,"text":"Education because we've so"},{"time":376000,"text":"dropped out of compassion."},{"time":378000,"text":"People often think it simply means"},{"time":380000,"text":"feeling sorry for somebody."},{"time":382000,"text":"But of course you don't understand compassion"},{"time":385000,"text":"if you're just going to think about it."},{"time":387000,"text":"You also have to do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":389000,"text":"I want them to get the media involved"},{"time":392000,"text":"because the media are crucial"},{"time":394000,"text":"in helping to dissolve some of the stereotypical views"},{"time":397000,"text":"we have of other people,"},{"time":399000,"text":"which are dividing us from one another."},{"time":401000,"text":"The same applies to educators."},{"time":404000,"text":"I'd like youth to get a sense of"},{"time":408000,"text":"the dynamism, the dynamic and challenge"},{"time":412000,"text":"of a compassionate lifestyle."},{"time":414000,"text":"And also see that it demands acute intelligence,"},{"time":417000,"text":"not just a gooey feeling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":420000,"text":"I'd like to call upon scholars to explore"},{"time":423000,"text":"the compassionate theme"},{"time":425000,"text":"in their own and in other people's traditions."},{"time":429000,"text":"And perhaps above all,"},{"time":431000,"text":"to encourage a sensitivity about"},{"time":435000,"text":"uncompassionate speaking,"},{"time":437000,"text":"so that because people have this Charter,"},{"time":440000,"text":"whatever their beliefs or lack of them,"},{"time":444000,"text":"they feel empowered"},{"time":446000,"text":"to challenge uncompassionate speech,"},{"time":450000,"text":"disdainful remarks"},{"time":452000,"text":"from their religious leaders, their political leaders,"},{"time":455000,"text":"from the captains of industry."},{"time":457000,"text":"Because we can change the world,"},{"time":459000,"text":"we have the ability."}]},{"cues":[{"time":462000,"text":"I would never have thought of putting the Charter online."},{"time":465000,"text":"I was still stuck in the old world"},{"time":467000,"text":"of a whole bunch of boffins sitting together in a room"},{"time":470000,"text":"and issuing yet another arcane statement."},{"time":473000,"text":"And TED introduced me to a whole new way"},{"time":476000,"text":"of thinking and presenting ideas."},{"time":478000,"text":"Because that is what is so wonderful about TED."},{"time":481000,"text":"In this room, all this expertise,"},{"time":486000,"text":"if we joined it all together,"},{"time":488000,"text":"we could change the world."},{"time":490000,"text":"And of course the problems sometimes seem insuperable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495000,"text":"But I'd just like to quote, finish at the end"},{"time":498000,"text":"with a reference to a British author, an Oxford author"},{"time":502000,"text":"whom I don't quote very often,"},{"time":504000,"text":"C.S. Lewis."},{"time":506000,"text":"But he wrote one thing that stuck in my mind"},{"time":508000,"text":"ever since I read it when I was a schoolgirl."},{"time":511000,"text":"It's in his book \"The Four Loves.\""},{"time":514000,"text":"He said that he distinguished between erotic love,"},{"time":518000,"text":"when two people gaze, spellbound, into each other's eyes."},{"time":524000,"text":"And then he compared that to friendship,"},{"time":527000,"text":"when two people stand side by side, as it were, shoulder to shoulder,"},{"time":531000,"text":"with their eyes fixed on a common goal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535000,"text":"We don't have to fall in love with each other,"},{"time":540000,"text":"but we can become friends."},{"time":543000,"text":"And I am convinced."},{"time":545000,"text":"I felt it very strongly"},{"time":548000,"text":"during our little deliberations at Vevey,"},{"time":552000,"text":"that when people of all different persuasions"},{"time":556000,"text":"come together, working side by side"},{"time":560000,"text":"for a common goal,"},{"time":562000,"text":"differences melt away."},{"time":564000,"text":"And we learn amity."},{"time":566000,"text":"And we learn to live together and to get to know one another."},{"time":571000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":573000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}